  "texts": [
    "This further validates the effectiveness of our MagicTime Recipe.",
    "A.4 Validation on Large Video Generative ModelsThe above baselines are conducted on SD1.5 (∼860M) and Open-Sora-Plan v1.0.0 (∼700M).",
    "We further select CogVideoX-5B [81] to show that the recipe can continue be effective when scaling to larger video generation models.",
    "Notably, CogVideoX-5B is among the few recent large models [81]- [83] that have publicly released training scripts.",
    "To integrate the MagicTime Recipe into the 3D Attention architecture of CogVideoX [81], we incorporate MagicAdapter-T and MagicAdapter-S into the first and last halves of the model layers, respectively."
  ],
